	 are looking for all lover of cars from Germany!Volkswagen\, Audi\, Merced
	es\, BMW and Porsche cars new and old.If you are a lover of these cars\, y
	ou know that it always seems that these cars are split up and only do bran
	d specific events. Well\, let’s break that tradition and just show up and 
	have fun!8403 Main St\, Edmonds\, WA 98026. \\( Caffe Ladro parking lot ar
	ea \\)9am to 11am\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/german-
	cars-and-coffee/18547095/2026-04-11T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Food & Drink
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/german-cars-and-coffee/18
	547095/2026-04-11T00
LOCATION:Caffe Ladro\, 8403 Main Street\, Edmonds\, WA
